ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectCanadian Food Agency - Public Service Alliance of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving the ENTRY by the Canadian Food Inspection Agency into a COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the PUBLIC SERVICE ALLIANCE OF CANADA (PSAC) that covers all employees of the PSAC Bargaining Unit for the period beginning on January 1, 2018 and ending on December 31, 2021.
